NLC India said on Wednesday the death toll from a boiler blast at the lignite miner and electricity generator's plant in the southern Tamil Nadu state rose to 13.Two people injured in the blast have been discharged, a senior company official said.The incident, which occurred last week when the unit was shut for maintenance, was the second deadly accident at the plant in two months.Reuters 
